summary:
- **Removal from mFund**: Smarter Money Fund - Assisted Investor Class (ASX: SMF01) will be delisted from the ASX's Managed Fund Settlement Service (mFund) at market close on **17 June 2025**.  
- **Reason**: Requested by Equity Trustees Limited under ASX Operating Rules (Rule 10A.3.1.(g)).  

*(Note: No material impact on trading/capital structure identified beyond delisting from mFund.)*
